title: HOME
credits: Welcome to Just Dance Best! Enjoy over 700 songs all for free.

credits_translation.tr: Just Dance Best'e hoş geldiniz! Artık 700'den fazla şarkının keyfini ücretsiz olarak çıkarabilirsiniz.
credits_translation.zh: 欢迎来到Just Dance Best！ 欣赏700多首歌曲。
credits_translation.ru: Добро пожаловать в Just Dance Best! Наслаждайтесь более чем 700 песнями.
credits_translation.es: ¡Bienvenido a Just Dance Best! Disfruta de más de 700 canciones.
credits_translation.pt: Bem-vindo ao Just Dance Best! Desfrute de mais de 700 músicas.
credits_translation.fr: Bienvenue dans Just Dance Best! Écoutez plus de 700 chansons.
